<div id="pf6f5" class="pf w16 h124" data-page-no="6f5"><div class="pc pc6f5 w16 h124"><div class="t m203 x11 h2b y203d ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">18 </div><div class="t m5 x4a h2b y203d ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">î˜‰</div><div class="t m2bb x96 h2b y2246 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LIFE </div><div class="t m59e x68 h34 y203f ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">OF CHRIST. </div><div class="t m7a9 x5d h2b y1b25 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m81b x60 h2b y132f ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did these men address the disciples ? </div><div class="t mb24 x11 h2b y15bb ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse </div><div class="t mae6 x4e h34 y1acb ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t m7a9 x5d h2b y1bbe ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14. </div><div class="t m2941 x60 h2b y1c73 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Having lost sight of Jesus, where did the </div><div class="t m153 x11 h2b y1ee8 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disciples go ? Verses 12, 13. </div><div class="t m7a9 x5d h2b y1bf1 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">15. </div><div class="t m1c56 x60 h2b y1720 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In what way did they occupy their time </div><div class="t m2942 x11 h2b y1cf6 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">while waiting for the promise of the Spirit? </div><div class="t m2cf x11 h2b y1b28 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 14. </div><div class="t m7a9 x5d h2b y1b29 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16. </div><div class="t m1225 x60 h2b y1354 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Are you waiting for the same promise ? </div><div class="t m70f x11 h2b y1ab1 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How is your time being spent, in view of it ? </div><div class="t m70f x11e ha0 y2247 ffa fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m2943 xbf h34 y220a ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rev. 7 </div><div class="t m874 xbf h34 y1b26 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Luke 24 : 52. </div><div class="t ma7c xbf h34 y1c08 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Luke 24 53. </div><div class="t ma7c x11e ha0 y2248 ffa fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"><span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m166b x84 h34 y195a ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">READING. </div><div class="t mb83 x5d h2b y10d3 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot; Desire of Ages,&quot; chapter 87. </div><div class="t m1857 x68 h2b y12f6 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE. </div><div class="t m1ee7 x5d h2b y1889 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Although Jesus had told His disciples plainly that He was </div><div class="t m52b x11 h2b y1be1 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">soon to go away, but would replace His personal presence with the </div><div class="t m1335 x11 h2b y195c ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit, they could not as yet so far divest themselves of the </div><div class="t m97a x11 h2b y418 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">common idea that the Messiah was to reign a temporal king, as to </div><div class="t m1fa4 x11 h2b y1afa ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">anticipate with satisfaction the coming of the Holy Spirit to them. </div><div class="t m12f6 x11 h2b y1e39 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">At this distance how strange it all seems, and yet they were no </div><div class="t md51 x11 h2b y1516 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blinder respecting that truth than many of us now are on other </div><div class="t m1335 x11 h2b y1da6 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">important subjects. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
